sql.sqlStatement:
SELECT '{'                  as [ITEM],
       'USA'                as [Label],
       'Border 1 Begin'     as [Style Name]

SELECT '{'   as [ITEM],
       'Northeast'          as [Label],
       'Border 3 Begin'     as [Style Name]

SELECT [State Code]         as [Item],
       [State Code]         as [Label],
       [State]              as [Outside Label]
FROM   [census regions$]
WHERE  [Region] = 'Northeast'

SELECT '{'   as [ITEM],
       'South'              as [Label],
       'Border 3 Begin'     as [Style Name]

SELECT [State Code]         as [Item],
       [State Code]         as [Label],
       [State]              as [Outside Label]
FROM   [census regions$]
WHERE  [Region] = 'South'

SELECT '{'   as [ITEM],
       'Midwest'            as [Label],
       'Border 3 Begin'     as [Style Name]

SELECT [State Code]         as [Item],
       [State Code]         as [Label],
       [State]              as [Outside Label]
FROM   [census regions$]
WHERE  [Region] = 'Midwest'

SELECT '{'   as [ITEM],
       'West'               as [Label],
       'Border 3 Begin'     as [Style Name]

SELECT [State Code]         as [Item],
       [State Code]         as [Label],
       [State]              as [Outside Label]
FROM   [census regions$]
WHERE  [Region] = 'West'

SELECT [StateCode]          as [Item],
       [NeighborStateCode]  as [Is Related To Item]
FROM   [neighbor state$]
